title: 2025 Elections Coverage | Fox News
description: Stay informed on the 2025 U.S. elections, including gubernatorial races in New Jersey and Virginia, state legislative elections, key mayoral contests in major cities, and special congressional elections.

Two New York lawmakers are blasting New York City mayor-elect Mamdani over a report that a member of his transition team has made controversial posts about Israel for years.
Mayor-elect Zohran Mamdani's office announced on Wednesday that Jessica Tisch will remain the New York City Police Department commissioner.
New York City Mayor-elect Zohran Mamdani, who won the city's mayoral race earlier this month, is fundraising for his transition, seeking a total of $4 million.
A New Jersey police sergeant and former Democratic candidate for state legislature was arrested for allegedly drugging and sexually assaulting a child he met online, prosecutors said.
New York City Mayor-elect Zohran Mamdani reaffirms that he would honor the International Criminal Court’s arrest warrant for Netanyahu if the Israeli prime minister visits the city.
Keith Michael Lisa of New Jersey was charged after a statewide manhunt for allegedly ransacking and vandalizing U.S. Attorney Alina Habba's Newark office with a baseball bat.
A Bronx judge warned she won’t approve a plea deal for David Mosley, an aspiring rapper accused of killing a cat in a satanic ritual, unless he faces the maximum penalty.
Columbia University professor Mahmood Mamdani discusses staying distant from his son Zohran Mamdani's mayoral administration, citing power's corrupting influence.
Nearly a dozen Democrats will vie for Mikie Sherrill's New Jersey House seat when she resigns, including former Rep. Tom Malinowski, as a special election looms.
A panel of three federal judges ruled that a congressional map passed by Texas lawmakers was "racially gerrymandered" and cannot go into effect Tuesday.
Former New York Jets star Brett Favre touched a bit on the shooting that left cornerback and special teams player Kris Boyd wounded. Police were searching for the gunman.
My walk through Virginia's historic Pocahontas Island, America's oldest free Black community, gave me new insights into restoring merit and faith in the American Dream.
Nassau County Executive Bruce Blakeman slammed Gov. Kathy Hochul's potential corporate tax increase, warning it would be a "disaster" for New York's economy.
Rep. Alexandria Ocasio-Cortez distanced herself from New York City Council member Chi Osse's effort to primary House Democratic Leader Hakeem Jeffries.
Political newcomer and former State Department expert David Williams enters race to unseat Democratic Sen. Mark Warner in Virginia's 2026 election.
Democrat-run cities like New York and San Francisco rank among America's most expensive, while Republican-led areas maintain lower living costs. That is very telling about "affordability."
Authorities seek public help identifying suspects in Virginia jackpotting scheme that netted nearly $200,000 from Apple Federal Credit Union ATM machine.
U.N. Ambassador Mike Waltz teams up with rapper Nicki Minaj to address Christian persecution in Nigeria in an unexpected collaboration that's making headlines.
Former Democratic National Committee vice chair David Hogg campaigned for Aftyn Behn in Tennessee's 7th Congressional District special election as Democrats aim to flip the deep-red seat.
Big Apple Police Commissioner Jessica Tisch spoke at a press conference to provide details about the shooting of a police officer on Monday morning
New York City Police Commissioner Jessica Tisch provided details about the Monday morning shooting of a police officer. (Credit: @nypd via YouTube)
Far-left Gen Z activist Chi Ossé filed paperwork against House Minority Leader Hakeem Jeffries, D-N.Y., marking a generational split within Democratic Party.
A federal judge criticized the DOJ for mishandling evidence in former FBI Director James Comey's case and warned the indictment could be dismissed due to tainted proceedings.
Podcaster Benny Johnson joins ‘Fox & Friends’ to discuss how Turning Point USA honored Charlie Kirk at a UFC event in New York City.
The NYPD released photos of a suspect in the shooting of New York Jets cornerback and special teams player Kris Boyd on Monday morning.
President Donald Trump announced a potential White House meeting with NYC Mayor-elect Zohran Mamdani despite threats to cut federal funding.
The Washington Post editorial board suggested Sunday that Seattle Mayor-elect Katie Wilson may be less restrained than New York City Mayor-elect Zohran Mamdani.
Deadly Newark shooting claims two lives, injures three others. Mayor calls incident 'senseless' as authorities search for suspect in South Ward attack.
Cities nationwide are cracking down on outdoor dining as pandemic freedoms end, with Washington, D.C., reportedly joining New York and Philadelphia in imposing steep fees.
A major Starbucks union strike on Thursday coincided with the chain's popular Red Cup Day as NYC's incoming mayor, Zohran Mamdani, backs a worker boycott.
